{"title":"给LYH写的操作手册","slug":"给LYH写的操作手册","date":"2018-11-21T13:42:26.000Z","updated":"2018-11-22T12:48:13.992Z","comments":true,"excerpt":"","content":"<h2 id=\"文章\"><a href=\"#文章\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"文章\"></a>文章</h2><h3 id=\"写作\"><a href=\"#写作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"写作\"></a>写作</h3><p><strong><u>新建Post</u></strong><br><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"> 1. <span class=\"built_in\">shift</span> + 鼠标右键 选择<span class=\"string\">'在此处打开PowerShell命令窗口'</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"> 2. window + R 输入 cmd -&gt; enter</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"> 3. 鼠标右键 Git Bash Here</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">cd Lyh_Blog</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo new \"your_article_name\"</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p><strong><u>编辑文章</u></strong><br>YMAL设置<br><figure class=\"highlight yml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">title:</span> <span class=\"string\">your_artilce_name</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">date:</span> <span class=\"string\">喵喵喵</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">comments:</span> <span class=\"literal\">true</span> <span class=\"comment\"># 是否开启评论功能， 默认true</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">thumbnail:</span> <span class=\"string\">'/img/article_img/this_article_pic.jpg'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">primarycolor:</span> </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"bullet\">    -</span> <span class=\"string\">red</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"bullet\">    -</span> <span class=\"string\">neal</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">accentcolor:</span> </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"bullet\">    -</span> <span class=\"string\">red</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"bullet\">    -</span> <span class=\"string\">lightblue</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>颜色设置<br>| 颜色       | Color      | 效果       |<br>|:———:|:———:|:———-:|<br>红| <span style=\"color:#F44336\">red</span> | <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/color-red-F44336.svg\" alt=\"\"><br>青绿|<span style=\"color:#00BCD4\">cyan</span> | <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/color-cyan-00BCD4.svg\" alt=\"\"><br>粉|<span style=\"color:#E91E63\">pink</span>  | <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/color-pink-E91E63.svg\" alt=\"\"><br>蓝|<span style=\"color:#2196F3\">blue</span> | <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/color-blue-2196F3.svg\" alt=\"\"><br>亮蓝|<span style=\"color:#03A9F4\">lightBlue</span> | <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/color-lightBlue-03A9F4.svg\" alt=\"\"><br>白|<span style=\"color:#f1f3f4,background-color:#000\">white</span> | <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/color-white-f1f3f4.svg\" alt=\"\"><br>深紫|<span style=\"color:#673AB7\">deepPurple</span> | <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/color-deepPurple-673AB7.svg\" alt=\"\"><br>紫|<span style=\"color:#9C27B0\">purple</span> |<img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/color-purple-9C27B0.svg\" alt=\"\"><br>靛蓝|<span style=\"color:#3F51B5\">indigo</span> | <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/color-indigo-3F51B5.svg\" alt=\"\"><